    <preface>
      <p class="center"><i>These notes relate to the Prisoners (Early Release) (Scotland) Act 2025 (asp 1)</i><br /><i>which received Royal Assent on 22 January 2025</i></p>
      <p class="center"><b>PRISONERS (EARLY RELEASE) (SCOTLAND) ACT 2025</b></p>
      <p class="center"><b>EXPLANATORY NOTES</b></p>
    </preface>
    <mainBody>
